OL,9,     Gshow, but two guests aren't
OL,10,     Gimpressed by the continental
OL,11,     Gbreakfast.
OL,12,G1340FFour in a Bed
OL,13,     GThe last visit of the week is to
OL,14,     Gthe Cadillac Kustomz Hotel on the
OL,15,     GIsle of Bute, where owners Brody
OL,16,     Gand Rima hope to rock their
OL,17,     Gguests' worlds with a music-
OL,18,     Gfilled retro retreat.
